data.description: MUST SEE:  This is a one  of a kind South Side home nested in the trees.  with a walkout basement.   The home has great architecture with vaulted ceilings, 5 bedrooms, 3 baths, spacious living room and family room with Wet Bar and a 2 car attached Garage.   Plenty of space for a large family.
